and cherry-picked it to 2.2.x-branch  &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/storm/commit/200803d34166d8444e5ea7ae7c64556c3c6e6169&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/storm/commit/200803d34166d8444e5ea7ae7c64556c3c6e6169&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
